  "description": [
    "12 Facts and Fascism By George Selcfes Review by MELVIN N McKENZIE II we take the one world view the global view of the peoples war against fascism the picture today is bright Fascism is being beaten back on every front and we can see hat the day of victory is near If we take the national view the tanorama is not so brilliant Vari ous fascist or semifascist organiza tions such as Peace Now and the National Economic Council are working overtime to discredit our war with the Axis and engineer a negotiated peace The commercial press and the radio have never printed an article or broadcast a program telling what fascism really is There is a reason for this Many of the pub lications themselves are part of our own fascism and the ones who are not cannot tell the truth because it is like pointing a dagger at their own heart Every American who believes in democracy owes it to himself to know his enemy Facta and Fascism goes far beyond the exposees of the smallfry fascists in America This book names the most powerful forces in Europe which organized the Fascist and Nazi parties and movements"
  ],
